  25 Apr 2015; Mike Gilbert <floppym@gentoo.org> livecd-tools-2.0.3.ebuild,
  livecd-tools-2.0.4.ebuild, livecd-tools-9999.ebuild:
  Replace links pointing at git.overlays.gentoo.org.

  03 Jun 2014; Rick Farina <zerochaos@gentoo.org> livecd-tools-2.0.4.ebuild:
  remove DEPEND, xz-utils is in @system and not a DEPEND per devmanual
  http://devmanual.gentoo.org/general-concepts/dependencies/index.html#implicit-
  system-dependency

  03 Jun 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> livecd-tools-2.0.4.ebuild:
  Add DEPEND for unpacking.

